  m_text: "Morning, Andy. Welcome to another beautiful day on the SUNSET16. You\u2019ve
    been assigned maintenance on Section C-12 of the ship again for the foreseeable
    future. Wire duty. It\u2019s up your alley as a Technician. Your efficiency ratings
    have been stellar these past 5 years. DOLOS is pleased."
